 wielopi\u0119trowy fa\u0142sz |trans-title = Szumowski criticise the EU: 'There is no European solidarity'. Which is false at many levels<!-- trans-title is the English translation --> | date= 2020-03-26 |newspaper= [[OKO.press]] | url= https://oko.press/szumowski-krytykuje-ue-nie-ma-tej-europejskiej-solidarnosci-to-wielopietrowy-falsz/ |quote= Bo jak by\u015bmy czekali na inne kraje, na Europ\u0119, na \u015bwiat, to by\u015bmy si\u0119 obudzili bez \u015brodk\u00f3w, a dooko\u0142a wszyscy by te \u015brodki sobie zakupili ... \u017beby by\u0142a jasno\u015b\u0107, to nie jest tak, \u017ce my ten sprz\u0119t mamy w Europie, \u017ce s\u0105 jego nieograniczone ilo\u015bci. ... Bo niestety tutaj centralne zakupy zawiod\u0142y, nie ma tej europejskiej solidarno\u015bci.  |accessdate=2020-03-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200326225848/https://oko.press/szumowski-krytykuje-ue-nie-ma-tej-europejskiej-solidarnosci-to-wielopietrowy-falsz/ |archivedate= 2020-03-26 |url-status=live <!-- live|dead|unfit|usurped --> |url-access = <!-- (subscription/registration/limited) default=free -->}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"EUCommission_rescEU\">{{cite web | title= COVID-19: Commission creates first ever rescEU stockpile of medical equipment | website= [[European Commission]] |date =2020-03-19 | url = https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/pl/ip_20_476 | accessdate = 2020-03-26 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200322164544/https://ec.europa.eu/commission/presscorner/detail/en/ip_20_476 |archivedate= 2020-03-26 |url-status=live <!-- live|dead|unfit|usurped --> |url-access = <!-- (subscription/registration/limited) default=free -->}}</ref>\n\n<!-- shift to Template:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/Poland medical cases\n<ref name=\"OKOpress_20Mar_24Mar_MZ2deaths\">{{cite news | last1= Zag\u00f3rski | first1= S\u0142awomir | language =pl | title= Lekarka z Warszawy: W\u0142adze nie informuj\u0105 o wszystkich zgonach na koronawirusa |trans-title = Warsaw Doctor: the government doesn't inform us about all coronavirus deaths | date= 2020-03-25 |newspaper= [[OKO.press]] | url= https://oko.press/lekarka-z-warszawy-rzad-nie-informuje-o-wszystkich-zgonach-na-koronawirusa/ |quote= We wspomnianym szpitalu MSWiA, kt\u00f3ry obecnie pe\u0142ni rol\u0119 szpitala zaka\u017anego, zmar\u0142y ostatnio 2 osoby. W pi\u0105tek zmar\u0142 pacjent po przyje\u017adzie z Austrii, wczoraj pacjentka psychiatryczna.  |accessdate=2020-03-27 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200327003349/https://oko.press/lekarka-z-warszawy-rzad-nie-informuje-o-wszystkich-zgonach-na-koronawirusa/ |archivedate= 2020-03-27 |url-status=live |url-access = }}</ref>\n-->\n\n<!-- shift to Template:2019\u201320 coronavirus pandemic data/Poland medical cases\n<ref name=\"OKOpress_19Mar_MZ1death_clarified\">{{cite news | last1= Zag\u00f3rski | first1= S\u0142awomir | language =pl | title= Niezg\u0142oszona \u015bmier\u0107 z powodu koronawirusa w szpitalu MSWiA. Rodzina pozostawiona bez pomocy [LIST] |trans-title = Unannounced death from the coronavirus in the Interior Ministry hospital. The family was left helpless [LETTER] | date= 2020-03-26 |newspaper= [[OKO.press]] | url= https://oko.press/niezgloszona-smierc-z-powodu-koronawirusa-w-szpitalu-mswia-rodzina-pozostawiona-bez-pomocy-list/ |quote= \u017badna informacja o \u015bmierci mojego ojczyma nie pojawi\u0142a si\u0119 w \u017cadnym komunikacie. ...  |accessdate=2020-03-27 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20200327004112/https://oko.press/niezgloszona-smierc-z-powodu-koronawirusa-w-szpitalu-mswia-rodzina-pozostawiona-bez-pomocy-list/ |archivedate= 2020-03-27 |url-status=live |url-access =  }}</ref>\n-->\n\n<ref name=\"GazWyb_MOH_to_censor_medicos\">{{cite news | language =pl | title= Ministerstwo Zdrowia chce kontrolowa\u0107 wypowiedzi wojew\u00f3dzkich konsultant\u00f3w medycznych |trans-title = The Minister of Health wants to control voivodeship medical consultants' freedom of speech<!-- tr